;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/JnbbWn0</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[PiercedViking]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>NOT GOING TO PRISON!!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/vZGED08</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ASFBWKL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Yesterday I told you all that I was being sentenced today. 

That the police wanted 2 years.

That I was charged with possession of a large amount of prescription drugs I shouldn't have.

Well I have been sentenced.

1 years prison suspended with 2 years probation.

£1000 fine.

I also am going to be monitored for 7 years due to the large amount and have to attend a lot of rehabilitation courses but I'm not I'm prison.

I feel so happy and close to having a happy break down.

Thank you all, the last 24hrs have been hell but your kind words kept me going.  

I'm planning to hopefully do 4 UK free pizza day delivery when I get paid because I want to pay this happiness forward.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/vZGED08</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[thetinymonarch]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>You're Fired ??‍♂️</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/kww1nDQ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/aY2pOXW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/kww1nDQ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DKMainMan]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>What a Catastrophe</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/w1ABP32</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Xiro0rF.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/w1ABP32</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Razade]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>This.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Iz7pzqo</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LQUdjX1.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Iz7pzqo</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[randomthingsonthenet]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>They don’t care about you</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/eG5ZGvr</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AzdNH9D.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/eG5ZGvr</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ginalynn8942]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Finely Tuned Friday MEME DUMP To Make You Exhale Through Your Nostrils #212</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/YoJYNxC</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4w8VGa6.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>1. One of the biggest L takes I've ever heard (1/2)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IF3kErd.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>2. One of the biggest L takes I've ever heard (2/2)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7lc19fM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>3. To be fair to my man, that body is holy</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ButGmgG.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>4. When Skynet takes over a Turkish kebab shop</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ShRHGci.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>5. "Oh shit, she ded, okay byeeeee..."</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1BlvOql.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>6. Dad uses this April Fool's Day to prank his daughters into believing school had just reopened</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/07Ti9hp.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>7</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/awEDqew.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>8. Wait...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GETd6Kc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>9.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/w9IqAuO.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>10</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SxIA4vx.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>11. Johnny Carson trolling Myrtle Young the world renown potato chip collector.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4lgX8Nc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>12. PEAR PRESSURE!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ptppC5w.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>13. The other day this guy on our team had 0 kills and 3 deaths and he was like "EZ" at the end of the match...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/k4hrvUB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>14. Good to see that a company is finally listening to its customers!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qJ6zdjZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>15.  It's so great to see an indie game succeed! Balatro just sold 5 million copies and it was made by just one guy. I find the story inspiring and in spirit of his message I would like to ask you to check out (and maybe wishlist) the indie game I'm currently working on, called: Do Not Press The Button (Or You'll Delete The Multiverse)

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2336120/Dont_Press_The_Button_To_Delete_The_Multiverse_The_Game/

P.S. Thank you for your support, it means the world to me and my brother! Game coming soon.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/YoJYNxC</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheseusGames]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Skills</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/okMJmTs</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GMaFxNV.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/okMJmTs</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Multipass]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Ding dong diddly dumperino</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/YBUdfN2</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vEB4Pfu.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ALjo3jQ.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZYZHrz6.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2I9OLzi.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Vq2pwA2.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HMj6dpL.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LxfZg6h.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6ahzsIy.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RNWVC4b.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JW2SqxF.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/e3OOIb1.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><